#helper function
pcaCharts <- function(x) {
    x.var <- x$sdev ^ 2
    x.pvar <- x.var/sum(x.var)
    print("Proportions of variance:")
    print(x.pvar)
    
    par(mfrow=c(1,2))
    screeplot(x, npcs = 12)
    plot(cumsum(x.pvar),xlab="Principal component", ylab="Cumulative Proportion of variance explained", ylim=c(0,1), type='b')
    par(mfrow=c(1,1))
    print("Cumulative proportions of variance:")
    print(cumsum(x.pvar))
}

mean = colMeans(pca_data)
cov = cov(pca_data)
ma_dist = mahalanobis(pca_data, mean, cov)
ma_dist = data.frame(cbind(1:length(ma_dist), ma_dist))
colnames(ma_dist) = c("Record", "dist")

## Reconstruct
finaldata.anon = h2o.anomaly(finaldata.dl, finaldata.hex, per_feature=TRUE)
err = as.data.frame(finaldata.anon)
ae_err = as.data.frame(cbind(Record = 1:nrow(err), ae_err = log10(apply(err, 1, sum))))
end = Sys.time()
end - start
